    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Wednesday about a $400 million donation to Columbia University from John Werner Kluge, who made his fortune from the Metromedia Company, referred imprecisely to the status of Metromedia's television stations after Mr. Kluge sold them. They became the core of the Fox broadcast network, not of Fox News.</p>
      </block>
